snippet.title: Symphony of the Stars - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Gameplay trailer for the upcoming release, Symphony of the Stars!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3187490/Symphony_of_the_Stars/

Explore a vast fantasy world in this top-down RPG. Sneak past enemies with overworld skills or engage them in strategic, turn-based combat. Solve puzzles and build the strength of your characters as an epic adventure unfolds!
